lid; background-color: #ccc;"> he said that a month ago</a>!) and (2) he is=
 planning to step down as Twitter CEO to spend more time at Tesla Inc. (sin=
ce, after all, he <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/=
30025450.287534/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2FzaGluZ3RvbnBvc3QuY29tL3RlY2hub2xvZ3kvMjA=
